{"tid":1962183,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"學術討論 究竟咩係愛情","createTime":"2020-04-07T09:58:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T04:50:00.000Z","uid":237060,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"59a3171456e3657bfff19cc12de6d26d3ef0dc9a","tid":1962183,"uid":237060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T09:58:43.000Z","msg":"聽得越多朋友嘅故事 就越覺得愛情戀愛關係唔多唔少都會充斥着謊言<br />\n<br />\n例如 講大話話自己喺屋企但其實出咗去蒲 同一面之緣嘅人出去飲酒但呃住女/男朋友<br />\n<br />\n睇住身邊拍咗八年拖嘅朋友都時不時講大話呃另一半 出去尋求一啲新鮮感刺激感<br />\n<br />\n我就越嚟越唔相信呢個世界係有愛情 所謂愛情其實只不過係兩個條件相近嘅人 睇大家順眼就一齊 好似冇咩話愛定唔愛 唔討厭就好了"},{"pid":"6ef600e723c333ec58379731c22b6eb894f2e4c7","tid":1962183,"uid":8419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T10:00:21.000Z","msg":"大話呢家嘢，有一次就會有二三四五次"},{"pid":"72316001fb2d8af335f54d635a2073f995757704","tid":1962183,"uid":237060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T10:00:26.000Z","msg":"廢事開喺感情台 好似有啲格格不入<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ae952f341c971484a6e3be6b57193336badb40b","tid":1962183,"uid":237060,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6ef600e723c333ec58379731c22b6eb894f2e4c7","tid":1962183,"uid":8419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T10:00:21.000Z","msg":"大話呢家嘢，有一次就會有二三四五次"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T10:01:59.000Z","msg":"冇錯呀 拍咗咁多年拖都隱瞞左五次以上 <br />\n其實結咗婚20幾年 可能就瞞足20幾年 其實愛情婚姻係咪就係謊言 只係睇吓你有冇發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"752e582dc083aad3e0ef78d1e4e637259c8ee4e7","tid":1962183,"uid":237060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T10:04:10.000Z","msg":"希望真係有人學術交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"435a556985c0ce2e2882c2b95ea9afc9dbecf4c2","tid":1962183,"uid":349608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T10:06:34.000Z","msg":"性就係愛情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da208a